rows.label: qst003901_msg0002
rows.name:
Are you the one the Chief
sent? You're here to help
fix the crane, right?

rows.label: qst003901_msg0004
rows.name:
It's a thick wire, but it
wasn't cut in one go.

rows.label: qst003901_msg0007
rows.name: Who benefits from delaying our work?

rows.label: qst003901_msg0008
rows.name:
...Whatever. I'll leave
finding the culprit to you.

rows.label: qst003901_msg0009
rows.name:
What I need are the materials
to reconnect the wire.

rows.label: qst003901_msg0011
rows.name:
If you salvage in Gula, you
should find a fair few.

rows.label: qst003901_msg0102
rows.name:
Five Winding Gears... You can
get them by salvaging in Gula.

rows.label: qst003901_msg0202
rows.name:
With these, I can fix
the crane... Thanks.

rows.label: qst003901_msg0203
rows.name: As for the one who cut it...

rows.label: qst003901_msg0204
rows.name:
Whatever. I'm just here
to fix this thing.
